svg.title: {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}\operatorname {P} [x_{j}]&={\sqrt {\frac {m\omega }{\pi \hbar }}}\int _{(j-1/2)\delta x}^{(j+1/2)\delta x}\exp \left(-{\frac {m\omega x^{2}}{\hbar }}\right)\,dx\\&={\sqrt {\frac {1}{\pi }}}\int _{(j-1/2)\delta x{\sqrt {m\omega /\hbar }}}^{(j+1/2)\delta x{\sqrt {m\omega /\hbar }}}e^{u^{2}}\,du\\&={\frac {1}{2}}\left[\operatorname {erf} \left(\left(j+{\frac {1}{2}}\right)\delta x\cdot {\sqrt {\frac {m\omega }{\hbar }}}\right)-\operatorname {erf} \left(\left(j-{\frac {1}{2}}\right)\delta x\cdot {\sqrt {\frac {m\omega }{\hbar }}}\right)\right]\end{aligned}}}
